    //temple
    "Event.Temple.0": "Have you ever been here?",
    "Event.Temple.1": "No? I see.$6",
    "Event.Temple.2": "This is an abandoned temple.",
    "Event.Temple.3": "Come with me.",
    "Event.Temple.4": "This place has been abandoned for a while...#$b#I understand the writing on the altars, though.#$b#Look, I'll show you.",
    "Event.Temple.5": "Javi gave you a copy of the scriptures!",
    "Event.Temple.6": "This statue though...I don't get what it's talking about.#$b#Maybe you can figure it out.",
    "Event.Temple.7": "Almost forgot.",
    "Event.Temple.8": "It depends on you if this place flourishes...or not.",

    //temple w/o Javi
    "Event.Temple.0_alt": "What's this place?",
    "Event.Temple.1_alt": "It seems abandoned.",
    "Event.Temple.2_alt": "You think you've seen this writing somewhere before...",
    "Event.Temple.3_alt": "You realize you can understand the language!",
    "Event.Temple.4_alt": "Now... It depends on you whether this place flourishes or not.",

    //intro
    "Event.Intro.1": "This will be quick.",
    "Event.Intro.2": "...or maybe not.",
    "Event.Intro.3": "Huff...#$b#This lava doesn't make it easier...",
    "Event.Intro.4": "Alright. That's done.",
    "Event.Intro.5": "What are you doing here!?",
    "Event.Intro.5qA": "I was following a monster...",
    "Event.Intro.5qB": "What are YOU doing here?",
    "Event.Intro.5qC": "...What was that?",
    "Event.Intro.6A": "Ye fell into its trap.#$b#That thing wanted to trap you here.#$b#If I were you, I'd head back.",
    "Event.Intro.6B": "None of your business.",
    "Event.Intro.6C": "A barrier.#$b#It keeps the monsters in the volcano.#$b#Some must've found how to break it...",
    "Event.Intro.7": "Is it your first time here?#$b#@...alright. Call me Javi, I live in the island southwest.",
    "Event.Intro.8":"I'll get going now.",
    "Event.Intro.9":"See you, @.",
    "Event.Intro.extra":"What brought you to this island?",
    "Event.Intro.extra2":"Stranded? What a shame.",
    "Event.Intro.10": "...Who is this person?",
    "Event.Intro.11": "You didn't know there were people on this island.",
    "Event.Intro.12": "This seems suspicious...",

    //2h
    "Javi2h.1":"Heh! Ye see that, landlubber?",
    "Javi2h.2":"I'm in a good mood, so c'mere.#$b#I'll tell ya a tale!",
    "Javi2h.3":"Ever heard of 'The Crimsonfish'?#$b#Nay, not the fish.#$b#Crimsonfish conquered gem sea with his cap'n, The Legend.#$b#Yes, like the fish too.",
    "Javi2h.4":"He joined young, no one thought he'd last.",
    "Javi2h.5":"Some say he was a poor kid,",
    "Javi2h.6":"Others, that he was a swindler...",
    "Javi2h.7":"Others, a kicked out navy member...#The rumours are endless.",
    "Javi2h.8":"But the tale of Crimsonfish started in that ship.",
    "Javi2h.9":"Yawn...come back another day. I'll have more rumours.",

    //4h
    "Javi4h.1":"We got a lot of fish today.",
    "Javi4h.2":"Can you bring these to the hut?",
    "Javi4h.3":"I need to grab something.",
    "Javi4h.4":"Someone's journal.",
    "Javi4h.Q":"Read it?",
    "Javi4h.Y":"Yes",
    "Javi4h.N":"No",
    "Javi4h.5":"@, open the door.",
    "Javi4h.6":"Thanks. Will you stay for dinner?",
    "Javi4h.7":"Javi prepared dinner.",
    "Javi4h.8":"The journal stays hidden away.",
    "Javi4h.9":"What was the diary talking about...?",
    "Javi4h.9.alt":"What could it have been...?",
    
    //4h - when you read diary
    "Javi4h.read.0": "The nightmares haven't stopped. I began this diary with the hopes it'll help.",
    "Javi4h.read.1": "I must tell everything from the start. Everything began with him. My father.",
    "Javi4h.read.1_cont":"He was part of the navy. In his free time he used to bring me to the sea.",
    "Javi4h.read.2": "You read a little further...",
    "Javi4h.read.3": "...But he obtained a high rank, and didn't have time for me anymore. We stopped having these moments.",
    "Javi4h.read.3_cont":"In my adulthood, I still yearned for the sea, and I decided to follow in his steps. I tried to enlist in the navy, but I was rejected by its men.",
    "Javi4h.read.4": "You read a little further...",
    "Javi4h.read.5": "...Then, I had to make a choice to save my life.#$b#I saw in piracy my escape. I joined a pirate ship under another identity.#$b#In my childhood I loved the sea, having sailed with my father. But... I never wanted it to be like this.#$b#Was life laughing in my face?",
    "Javi4h.read.6": "It was hard to survive in that ship.#Everyone fought for control.#You were on your own.#But I didn't need anyone. I never did.",
    "Javi4h.read.7": "...",
    "Javi4h.read.8": "I barely survived my first fight.#Then I met him.",
    "Javi4h.read.8.GINPCTweaks": "I barely survived my first fight.#Then I met her.",
    "Javi4h.read.9": "CAPTAIN: I told you.#CAPTAIN: No one dies in their first battle.",
    "Javi4h.read.9.GINPCTweaks": "CAPTAIN: I told you.#CAPTAIN: No one dies in their first battle.",
    "Javi4h.read.10": "Back then, I didn't understand why he did it.",
    "Javi4h.read.10.GINPCTweaks": "Back then, I didn't understand why she did it.",
    "Javi4h.read.altend":"Better stop there for today.",

    //6h 
    "Javi6h.1": "Yer here again. Came back for another story?",
    "Javi6h.2":"Hahaha, sure. C'mere landlubber, I'll tell ya somethin' new!",
    "Javi6h.3":"The Legend took that boy under his fin.",
    "Javi6h.3.GINPCTweaks":"The Legend took that boy under her fin.",
    "Javi6h.4":"He supposedly saw hidden potential in him...we complained, but the respect for our cap'n made us give in.",
    "Javi6h.4.GINPCTweaks":"She supposedly saw hidden potential in him...we complained, but the respect for our cap'n made us give in.",
    "Javi6h.5":"Keeping track of the supplies, handling pirates' disputes...",
    "Javi6h.6":"With time, he got the hang of it.",
    "Javi6h.7":"Many years passed. He'd become a seasoned member of the ship. The captain trusted him to get the crew to listen. And us, to keep him in check.",
    "Javi6h.8":"If a problem happened, he was to be called.",
    "Javi6h.9":"The kid showed competence, and won the crew's approval.",
    "Javi6h.10": "Sometimes, we saw no ships for days, but the crew would find something to do. Dividing the loot, gambling...",
    "Javi6h.10.lighter": "Sometimes, we saw no ships for days, but the crew would find something to do. Dividing the loot, playing cards...",
    "Javi6h.11":"We had no reason to go back to land.",
    "Javi6h.12":"But...",
    "Javi6h.QA":"You're stopping at that?",
    "Javi6h.QB":"Stop pushing",
    "Javi6h.AA":"...#$b#Very well.#$b#After that, a tragedy occurred in the ship.#$b#I was but a lad when it happened, yet...#$b#I still shiver at the memory.",
    "Javi6h.AB":"Bien hecho.",
    "Javi6h.13":"This old seadog has nothing else to tell you.",
    
    //8h
    "Javi8h.1":"One night, a naval ship took us by surprise.",
    "Javi8h.2":"They were known for catching pirates.#$b#We weren't going to give in so easily.#$b#And a fight began.", 
    "Javi8h.3":"I was cornered during the battle.",
    "Javi8h.4":"I knew I'd die.",
    "Javi8h.4.lighter":"I knew that was it for me.",
    "Javi8h.lighter":"But then...he saved me.", //alt is for the lighter backstory. it replaces '5'
    "Javi8h.lighter.GINPCTweaks":"But then...she saved me.", //alt is for the lighter backstory. it replaces '5'
    "Javi8h.5":"I saw the captain in front of me. I was used to bloodshed, but... I...",
    "Javi8h.5.GINPCTweaks":"I saw the captain in front of me. I was used to bloodshed, but... I...",
    "Javi8h.6":"He pushed me off the ship. I went to grab him so we wouldn't separate, but it was too late.",
    "Javi8h.6.GINPCTweaks":"She pushed me off the ship. I went to grab her so we wouldn't separate, but it was too late.",
    "Javi8h.7":"Where am I?",
    "Javi8h.8": "...When I realized, I had a necklace of the captain's tight in my hand.",
    "Javi8h.8.GINPCTweaks": "...When I realized, I had a necklace of the captain's tight in my hand.",

    "Javi8h.9":"The first days I was here...I couldn't stomach anything.",
    "Javi8h.9.lighter":"The first days I was here...I couldn't feel anything.",
    "Javi8h.10":"I don't know how much time passed.",
    "Javi8h.11":"My hair grew back, but I couldn't cut it.",
    "Javi8h.12":"Just looking at the sword made me sick.",
    "Javi8h.13":"The nights were even worse. I'd dream of the ship and the captain, just to wake up here.",
    "Javi8h.13.GINPCTweaks":"The nights were even worse. I'd dream of the ship and the captain, just to wake up here.",
    "Javi8h.14":"I never found out if anyone else survived.",
    "Javi8h.15":"\\\"If you don't care for yourself, no one will.\\\" That's what my father used to tell me. So why did he..?",
    "Javi8h.15.GINPCTweaks":"\\\"If you don't care for yourself, no one will.\\\" That's what my father used to tell me. So why did she..?",
    "Javi8h.16":"It made no sense.",
    "Javi8h.17":"There must've been some hidden reason. Right?",
    "Javi8h.18":"Because if I'm wrong, it means that...",
    "Javi8h.19":"I realized what I'd lost too late.",
    "Javi8h.20":"How much did you read?",
    "Javi8h.21":"Sit down.",
    "Javi8h.22":"...I'm disappointed, @.",
    "Javi8h.Q":"I didn't expect it from you.",
    "Javi8h.QA": "It was an accident, I swear!",
    "Javi8h.QB": "I'm sorry...I shouldn't have done it.",
    "Javi8h.QC": "If you're writing, it's meant to be read.",
    "Javi8h.AA": "You pick up a book 'by accident' multiple times?",
    "Javi8h.AB": "Yet you still did.",
    "Javi8h.AC": "Not everything is for you, @. Keep your hands off my things.",
    "Javi8h.23": "Guess there's no point hiding it now.",
    "Javi8h.2QA": "You were a pirate...",
    "Javi8h.2QB": "You knew Birdie's husband all along?",
    "Javi8h.2QB.GINPCTweaks": "You knew Birdie all along?",
    "Javi8h.2QC": "...",
    "Javi8h.2AA": "Bah. That was long ago.",
    "Javi8h.2AA2":"I don't care about it anymore.",
    "Javi8h.2AA3":"I'm just living off the island.",
    "Javi8h.2AB": "Aye. He was the captain of that ship.",
    "Javi8h.2AB.GINPCTweaks": "Aye. She was the captain of that ship.",
    "Javi8h.2AB2":"I recognized her from the pictures.",
    "Javi8h.2AC": "What, you're getting all shy now?",
    "Javi8h.24": "I heard she was searching for him.",
    "Javi8h.25": "She thinks the sea took him... she doesn't know what happened.",
    "Javi8h.24.GINPCTweaks": "I heard she was searching for something.",
    "Javi8h.25.GINPCTweaks": "She must think I never survived... she doesn't know what happened.",
    "Javi8h.3Q": "He should've survived instead...",
    "Javi8h.3Q.GINPCTweaks": "I'm indebted to her...",
    "Javi8h.3QA": "He's not here anymore. Just get over it.",
    "Javi8h.3QA.GINPCTweaks": "It was years ago. Just get over it.",
    "Javi8h.3QB": "You shouldn't hide like this.",
    "Javi8h.3QC": "Don't say that. He saved you for a reason.",
    "Javi8h.3QC.GINPCTweaks": "She saved you for a reason.",
    "Javi8h.3AA": "@, shut up.",
    "Javi8h.3AA2":"You think it's easy?",
    "Javi8h.3AA3":"You live in a farm. You've never sailed.",
    "Javi8h.3AB": "I've lived by lying, you're a little late for that.",
    "Javi8h.3AB2":"...",
    "Javi8h.3AC": "And he's gone.",
    "Javi8h.3AC.GINPCTweaks": "...",
    "Javi8h.3AC2": "But is it fine to keep her in the unknown?",
    "Javi8h.3AC3": "If I can't repay him... I owe his wife some closure.",
    "Javi8h.3AC3.GINPCTweaks": "I owe her closure. Who knows if she still remembers as vividly as I do.",
    "Javi8h.26": "Maybe it's better this way.",
    "Javi8h.27": "I'm over it.",
    "Javi8h.4QA": "Then why are you hiding?",
    "Javi8h.4QB": "Then why make a journal?",
    "Javi8h.4AA": "...",
    "Javi8h.4AB": "...That's just to put my mind at ease. Nothing else.",

    //10h
    "Javi10h.1": "@, you're here.",
    "Javi10h.2":"I have something to tell you.#$b#I'm planning to tell Birdie the truth, but...",
    "Javi10h.Q": "Javi: I don't know if it's the right choice.",
    "Javi10h.QA":"You should do it.",
    "Javi10h.QB":"It's a bad idea.",
    "Javi10h.AA": "Thanks, @.",
    //branching - bad ending
    "Javi10h.BadEnding.0": "...",
    "Javi10h.BadEnding.1": "I see. I could hurt her by telling her the truth.#$b#It's better if she thinks the sea took him.",
    "Javi10h.BadEnding.1.GINPCTweaks": "I see. I could hurt her by telling her the truth.",
    "Javi10h.BadEnding.2": "That was everything, @. I'll go home.",
    //branching - leads into either good or bad end depending on player's choices
    "Javi10h.AreYouSure.1":"@...#$b#I know you might have doubts about this.#$b#But...something in me tells me I should do it.",
    "Javi10h.AreYouSure.Q":"¿Should I backtrack?",
    "Javi10h.AreYouSure.QA":"Yes.",
    "Javi10h.AreYouSure.QB":"On second thought, you should tell her.",
    //branching - good ending
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.1":"Got it.#$b#Come with me, I want you to see her.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.2":"If I'm sure of what I'll do? Yes.#$b#I'm not taking it back.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.3":"Hello, my dear...#$b#Did you bring company?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.4":"Oh, what a coincidence.#$b#I came to see if there was anything new by the shore.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.5":"Hello.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.6":"Ah, you must be the person who lives in the southwest...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.Q":"Maybe you should help Javi...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.QA":"What's that shipwreck?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.QB":"Birdie, what was your husband like?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.QB.GINPCTweaks":"Birdie, what was your life like?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.QC":"Birdie, since when are you here?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.AA":"What are you trying, @?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.AB":"@...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.AC":"Gosh...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.Q2":"You should leave.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.Q2A":"Naw.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.Q2B":"Alright.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.A2A":"@. Leave.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.7":"So that's what happened...I understand.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.8":"I'm sorry about your husband.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.8.GINPCTweaks":"I'm sorry about your ship.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.9":"...#$b#Ma'am, there's something you should know.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.10":"Yes?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.11":"Your husband wore a golden necklace, right?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.11.GINPCTweaks":"You used to wear a golden necklace, right?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.12":"...How do you know?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.13":"...#$b#I used to know him.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.13.GINPCTweaks":"...#$b#I used to know you.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.14":"...I didn't catch your name. What's your name, dear?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.15":"My name is Javiera.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.16":"It can't be...$2#$b#How...?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.17":"My captain's quartermaster was called Javier, but he was a man...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.17.GINPCTweaks":"My quartermaster was called Javier, but he was a man...",
    //key n°18 is "dots"
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.19":"That's how. I faked my identity.#$b#You deserved to know what happened that night.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.20":"I'll leave.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.21":"Wait.$2#$b#I thought nobody had survived...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.22":"It's all thanks to him.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.22.GINPCTweaks":"It's all thanks to you.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.23":"He may not be here anymore, but...#$b#He'll stay in our memories. No one can take that away from us.#$b#I won't forget him.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.23.GINPCTweaks":"The crew may not be here anymore, but...#$b#They'll stay in our memories. No one can take that away from us.#$b#I won't forget them.",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.24":"Tell me...#$b#What was he like as a captain?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.24.GINPCTweaks":"Tell me...#$b#What do you remember?",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.25":"Let's see...",
    "Javi10h.GoodEnding.ConversationTopic":"I wasn't sure about doing it, but you gave me the final push. Thanks, @.",

    //12
    "Javi12h.1":"@.",
    "Javi12h.2":"I'm just paying a visit.",
    "Javi12h.3":"To think that the ship ended up here...",
    "Javi12h.4":"Birdie's still processing everything.",
    "Javi12h.5":"I don't know if it was right to tell her the truth.",
    "Javi12h.6":"But I owe one to the captain. If I can't make it up to him, I should bring his wife closure.",
    "Javi12h.6.GINPCTweaks":"But I owe one to her. I should bring her closure.",
    "Javi12h.7":"It feels like a weight has been lifted.",
    "Javi12h.8":"I'm still mad you'd read my journal behind my back.",
    "Javi12h.9":"But...things worked out fine because of that.",
    "Javi12h.10":"Take care, @.",
    "Javi12h.end":"After that, the pirate disappeared.#The man that talked about Javi...#Seems like he'd vanished.#Ghosts also stopped appearing in the ship.",
    "Javi12h.end.cont":"Was it...?#It'll never be known.",

    //12h - bad ending continuation
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.0": "@. What a coincidence.#$b#And to think the ship ended up here...",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.1": "...",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.2": "@, I've made a decision.#$b#I'll hand myself in to the navy.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.3": "After our conversation, I've been thinking about what's right.#$b#And...#$b#If he didn't survive, and I can't even help his wife...then I should hand myself in.#$b#This is my punishment.#$b#At least when I'm in jail I'll feel like I've done something right in my life.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.3.GINPCTweaks": "After our conversation, I've been thinking about what's right.#$b#And...#$b#If nobody else survived, and I can't even help her...then I should hand myself in.#$b#This is my punishment.#$b#At least when I'm in jail I'll feel like I've done something right in my life.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.4": "Who knows, I might see that man's face again.#$b#I mean my old man. Remember, he's part of the navy.#$b#And I... I joined the pirates.$4#$b#Definitely, this is my punishment for everything I've done.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.5": "Goodbye, @. This will be the last time we see each other.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.6": "After that, I never saw Javi again.#I still see pirates' spirits roam the ship, in eternal suffering.",
    "Javi12h.BadEnding.7": "...#And if things had been different? What if...?#Well, it doesn't make sense to wonder that now.",

    //bundle event: cooking
    "Event.Bundle.Cooking_1":"You passed the test with flying colors.",
    "Event.Bundle.Cooking_2":"Let's see about a reward.",
    "Event.Bundle.Cooking_3":"You unlocked new recipes!",

    //bundle event: fishing
    "Event.Bundle.Fishing_1":"A helmet was added to your Powers tab!",
    "Event.Bundle.Fishing_2":"You can now dive underwater. Maybe you should check the water by the sunken ship...",
    "Event.Bundle.Fishing_3":"You also received fishing implements.",
    "Event.Bundle.Fishing_4":"Wonder what's hidden underwater...",
    
    //bundle event: all done
    "Event.Bundle.Finish_1":"Well, well, well... you made it.",
    "Event.Bundle.Finish_2":"These things seem more lively than before.",
    "Event.Bundle.Finish_3":"The birds are very happy!",
    "Event.Bundle.Finish_3_inter1_alt":"Why is Leo here? He should be in Pelican Town.",
    "Event.Bundle.Finish_3_inter1":"Hey. Who brought Leo here?",
