    /* Pirate stories */
    /* I tried to make him sound like a stereotypical pirate here. */
    "RandomPirateStory_Monday":"Landlubber! I'll tell ya a secret.#I used to be in The Legend's ship.#Ruthless crew, I tell ya.#An' their quartermaster? A ladies' man like no other.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Tuesday": "Ye came back for more? I'll tell ya.#T'was a lad who'd just joined, first fight.#Shakin' like a leaf! Ha ha.#Ye know what the quartermaster said?#'No one dies on their first fight'.#Wonder who told 'im that.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Wednesday":"The cap'n depends on his quartermaster ta' keep mutiny under control.#We used ta' worry he'd go mad with power...But Javier knew how to keep 'im in check.#Remember, landlubber: Quartermaster's duty is to a crew, not to his cap'n.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Thursday":"Ye know what they call us?#\"Enemy of all mankind\"!#Pirates are hardened men.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Friday":"We live life as we see fit.#'S the good thing about bein' a pirate.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Saturday":"Despite what others may tell you...#Pirates are democratic, aye.#The cap'n is voted by a crew.",
    "RandomPirateStory_Sunday":"Pirates are judged by skill, aye.#And nothing else.",
